        "content": "<p>Hi. I have the following code:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">p</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ℚ</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"o\">]}</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">p</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">3</span> <span class=\"bp\">/</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">X</span> <span class=\"bp\">^</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">p.support</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">begin</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">rw</span> <span class=\"n\">finset.ext_iff</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">intro</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- a ∈ p.support ↔ a ∈ {0, 2}</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>And I would like to prove the goal by applying <code>cases</code>, splitting on whether <code>a ∈ {0, 2}</code> or not. How can I do this?<br>\n(My plan afterwards it to split the polynomial into <code>sum</code> of many monomials, then <code>p.coeff n = sum (pi.coeff n)</code>, which is <code>0</code> if <code>n</code> is not in {0, 2}.</p>",
